<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
      All current modules stay free!
    </p>

    <h4>Headline Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Unified Condition Engine with 41 fields and nested boolean logic</li>
      <li>Visual Condition Builder UI with presets</li>
      <li>Cinematic Time Skip with animated PixiJS overlay</li>
      <li>Chronicle Timeline View</li>
      <li>Note Viewer with filters, search, and bulk operations</li>
      <li>Calendar Fog of War with progressive revelation</li>
      <li>Multi-Calendar Sync and Secondary Calendar Viewer</li>
      <li>39 Text Enrichers for embedding live calendar data</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>New</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Note Sheet redesign with 5-tab layout and per-user ownership</li>
      <li>Category Manager with defaults, overrides, and presets</li>
      <li>Event duration, multi-day banners, and 3 display styles</li>
      <li>Festival system — calendar festivals auto-create as notes</li>
      <li>3-level event visibility: Visible, Hidden, Secret</li>
      <li>Lunar and solar eclipse calculation engine</li>
      <li>Randomized moon phases with anchor overrides</li>
      <li>Intraday weather with 4 time-of-day periods</li>
      <li>6 global theme presets across all apps</li>
      <li>3 new bundled calendars: Imperial, Golarion (IC), Pact Standard</li>
      <li>All 20 bundled calendars now include default climate zones</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Improvements</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>View permissions and combat behavior for all 7 widgets</li>
      <li>Weather FX Mode dropdown (Full, Reduced, Off)</li>
      <li>BigCal viewport capping with scrollable content</li>
      <li>Starfinder 2E world clock sync</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
